            <title><![CDATA[【[哆啦A梦笑]#冬季预防心脑血管疾病要注意保暖#】#冬季进补要适度# 医生提示，冬季气温低，老年人一定要结合自身实际条件，正确保暖，预防心脑血管疾病，尤其要...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哆啦A梦笑]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/doraemon/dr_10xiao-18fff9f7d5.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%86%AC%E5%AD%A3%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E5%BF%83%E8%84%91%E8%A1%80%E7%AE%A1%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BF%9D%E6%9A%96%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%86%AC%E5%AD%A3%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E5%BF%83%E8%84%91%E8%A1%80%E7%AE%A1%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BF%9D%E6%9A%96%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#冬季预防心脑血管疾病要注意保暖#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%86%AC%E5%AD%A3%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%A5%E8%A6%81%E9%80%82%E5%BA%A6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%86%AC%E5%AD%A3%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%A5%E8%A6%81%E9%80%82%E5%BA%A6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#冬季进补要适度#</span></a> 医生提示，冬季气温低，老年人一定要结合自身实际条件，正确保暖，预防心脑血管疾病，尤其要重视手部、头部、面部的保暖。此外，人体最适宜的环境温度是19至24摄氏度，过冷或者过热都会对心脑血管产生影响👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6jx19MH" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
